    <h2>3. Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>All original content (guides, articles, images) on this site is our property unless otherwise noted. Game names, logos, and screenshots are property of their respective owners and used for commentary and educational purposes under fair use.</p>

    <h2>4. User Conduct</h2>
    <p>When using our site, you agree not to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Scrape or republish our content without permission</li>
      <li>Use automated tools to access the site in a way that degrades service</li>
